Paste this:

@echo off title Owner Rawr64 Compiler echo Now Compiling "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java echo Finished Compiling pause

It should look like this

Make sure you have downloaded the latest JDK.

If you do not know, that means java development kit, update 11

“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
